浣熊發威 操控地洞搞破壞
How deep does this hole go?

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Donut County is an absolute treat. You drag holes across land to collect bigger and bigger aboveground objects, from puddles and fire pits to trees and boulders. New ideas change gameplay in intriguing ways, and concepts never overstay their welcome, making every puzzle feel new and interesting. The consequences of every hole you control propel a wonderfully quirky story about a suddenly subterranean society seeking a return to the surface. Along with the game’s fantastic visual style and marvelous soundtrack, its every idiosyncrasy miraculously blends into an inviting, cohesive whole.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Geneva Hodgson: Story editor, Donut County
